text = "The Council of Mages convenes in silence. The Binding Spell is cast — a flash of blinding light erupts across the Grand Hall. The ancient magic tears through reality itself. Telvar has succeeded... but at a terrible cost. He is pulled through the rift alongside Myramar, banished to the forgotten realm of Antica. Their fates are now intertwined, bound by the very spell meant to save them all."

